values: Life is sooo boring. I want to go on an adventure....

I want to name them. ^^ I love the name Myles, or Miles, it could be spelled either way, but i love that name for a little boy ^^. And for a little girl, there are two names i really love for a girl, Jenna, and Willow. I think those names are very pretty ^^

Yeah, so0 i go online today, and im just posting crap on Gaiaonline, and here, when my ex im's me with a new account ( I blocked her old one) and her display pic is of her getting boned by her new bf (the one she ran off with when we went to six flags) and she just keeps going on and on about how great sex is and how he's so great and so on. Then she says all her girl friends now hate me because she told them to hate me. Then i get s crap load of hate mail. Aren't I a lucky boy? ....Why do i live? But it seems things like this are out of my reach.

You need love.
You are a pretty normal, well-rounded person
that just craves that fairy tale love where you
will be swept off your feet and live happily
ever after. Chances are that you fantasize or
dream about it so much that you either see all
the guys/girls as unromantic or you tell
yourself that anyone could be your soulmate.
You long to have someone by your side and you
want to give back on the romance part too, not
just give.

My Senior project is done, and i have an extended lunch now ^-^. I can't wait until graduation is finished so i may start my little summer adventure.

Ok, i dunno, i was feeling depressed again. Different reasons, but anyways, i dunno, i was thinking about death. I dont ever wanna die. When i find that special girl I love, i want to live and be with her forever. I've decided upon research i've done (yes, i do research things, and like yeah. it's weird.) I need to find the Holy Grail and the Spear of Longinus (or the Spear of Destiny) Legends hold that these items give whoever has them immortality. Also it may give me the power to choose the fate of the world. I want to research more, but it is very difficult to get text on these items, their whereabouts, and whatever other legends are tied with them. I guess i'm being a pyscho now. So i'll stop writing about that. Um, lets see, today I got in an hour of practice driving. Then, basically hung out at home.

I freaked out, there was also a some paper there too, my dad was laughing when he saw it. So i cleaned it up and threw it away. It scard the shot outta me though.

Yupp, today i went to the mall to shop fro my dad. I got him one of the fancy smancy lazer massage thingies, and a nice leather jacket. It was kinda lonely there cuz i went to the mall alone. No one to really talk to. Heh, i need friends XP. Oh well. Let's then i just walked the mall, window shopping of course. Later on, my dad let me drive my car around the block for a little training. It was fun. I so cannot totally wait until i get my liscence! Yay! that will be so awesome! Oh Lolly, you can probably expect me and Chelsea to go and visit you. Let's all get wasted together!
I have a frekin car waiting for me, i just need to do the driving portion to get my liscence. Once i gets it, i'm outty. I'm gonna go and drive as far as possible.
